526-500 West 153rd Street, west of, adjoining, and at the S.W. corner of Amsterdam Avonue. St. Catherine's Roman Catholic Church and Rectory adjoins the corner; the Washington Eeights Methodist Episcopal Church is at the corner. The rest of the buildings
on this block are all three-story frame houses.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 377.
